addConfig

public PSRelationshipConfig addConfig(String name,
                                      String type)
Creates a 'User' relationship configuration with the specified name and adds that to this list. The configuration will have default system properties.

Parameters:
name - the name of the config, may not be null or empty. Must be unique among this collection of configurations. Can use getConfig(String) to check for uniqueness of the configuration name.
type - the type of the rel config, RS_TYPE_SYSTEM or RS_TYPE_USER, may not be null or empty.
Returns:
the added relationship config, never null
Throws:
IllegalArgumentException - if name is invalid.

Throws:
IllegalArgumentException - if name is not valid or it represents a system configuration.
